          <li>Natural oil resistance</li>
          <li>Beautiful wood grain</li>
          <li>Good dimensional stability</li>
          <li>No chemical treatment needed</li>
        </ul></div>
        <div class="gbb-cons"><div class="gbb-cons-title">CONS</div><ul>
          <li>Optional staining every 2-3 years</li>
          <li>Moderate price point</li>
          <li>Weathers to silver-gray if unsealed</li>
        </ul></div>
