      <div class="gbb-summary-grid">
        <div class="gbb-summary-item"><strong>Pressure Treated Pine</strong><span>Budget projects, side yards</span></div>
        <div class="gbb-summary-item"><strong>Western Red Cedar</strong><span>Beautiful natural look, great value</span></div>
        <div class="gbb-summary-item"><strong>Northern White Cedar</strong><span>Premium longevity, best investment</span></div>
      </div>
